SQL_STMT_U.val: select mqdt_mqty_id, case when not(code_ul.code_language is null) then code_ul.code_description else code_gb.code_description end, count(*) from :1/mqdt left join :1/code code_gb on code_gb.code_type=30 and code_gb.code_numbern=mqdt_mqty_id and code_gb.code_language='GB' left join :1/code code_ul on code_ul.code_type=30 and code_ul.code_numbern=mqdt_mqty_id and code_ul.code_language=':2' where :8 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 group by mqdt_mqty_id, case when not(code_ul.code_language is null) then code_ul.code_description else code_gb.code_description end order by mqdt_mqty_id
select MQDT_USRID, cast(count(*) as decimal(16,0)) from :1/MQ_DETAIL where :8 :2 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 GROUP BY MQDT_USRID
select MQDT_DEPT_CODE from :1/MQDT where MQDT_MQTY_ID = :2 and :8 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 group by MQDT_DEPT_CODE
